; Pin the public npm registry. We use only public packages, but Dependabot's
; automatic-github-packages-auth injects npm.pkg.github.com as a "private registry"
; and then aborts npm file-fetching ("Private npm registries require either a .npmrc
; file in your repository, or explicit scope/replaces-base configuration"). This .npmrc
; satisfies that check so Dependabot can still fetch npm files for *security* updates
; (npm version-updates were dropped — Expo lockstep; see .github/dependabot.yml). No secrets.
registry=https://registry.npmjs.org/
